extendedInfo.description: A collection of Hilarious Indian / Pakistani Jokes. Browse through the collection of funny Desi jokes written in shorthand, and use the sms option to copy to a text message so you can send them to your friends!Contains some of the best Sardar and Pathan Jokes!Most of the Jokes are written in Urdu / Hindi so be warned before you download this that unless you come from a south asian back ground you may not get it!PLEASE NOTE! This application contains language that may not be suitable for children!If you have any issues whatsoever please feel free to email us on Disharinc@hotmail.co.ukI would appreciate your feedback and will endevour to make this application more suitable for you.
